2016年2月28日，《[[約翰奧利佛之昔日新聞報報|约翰·奥利弗上周今夜秀]]》播出第三季第三集，也是全剧第62集，其中包含以[[唐納·川普|唐納·川普]]为主题的22分钟节目<ref name="nydn20160321" />。奥利弗在节目主要部分开始时引入[[2016年唐納·川普競選美國總統|特朗普竞选总统]]的话题。谈及候选人在共和党选民中的支持率堪称[[黑马|黑马]]时奥利弗称，支持他的这些选民一般不在总统大选中投票，就像“美国背上的[[黑素细胞痣|黑痣]]”，“一年前或许无伤大雅，现在却大到吓人，已经不能再忽视。”<ref name="youtube-lwt20160228">{{cite AV media | url = https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DnpO_RTSNmQ | title = Donald Trump | date = 2016-02-28 | publisher = [[HBO|HBO]] | via = [[YouTube|YouTube]] | last = Oliver | first = John | author-link = 约翰·奥利弗 | accessdate = 2020-09-08 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160815200430/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DnpO_RTSNmQ | archivedate = 2016-08-15 }} {{Wayback|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DnpO_RTSNmQ |date=20160815200430 }}</ref><ref name="huffpo">{{cite news | title = John Oliver Demolishes 'Serial Liar' Donald Trump | url = https://www.huffpost.com/entry/donald-drumpf-john-oliver_n_56d40adee4b0bf0dab32a73c | newspaper = [[赫芬顿邮报|The Huffington Post]] | date = 2016-02-29 | accessdate = 2020-09-08 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200628150032/https://www.huffingtonpost.ca/entry/donald-drumpf-john-oliver_n_56d40adee4b0bf0dab32a73c?ri18n=true | archivedate = 2020-06-28 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | title = The rise of American authoritarianism | url = https://www.vox.com/2016/3/1/11127424/trump-authoritarianism | first = Amanda | last = Taub | website = [[Vox|Vox]] | publisher = [[沃克斯传媒|Vox Media]] | date = 2016-03-01 | accessdate = 2020-09-08 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160329080808/http://www.vox.com/2016/3/1/11127424/trump-authoritarianism | archivedate = 2016-03-29 }}</ref>

