ld-drumpf-again/ }}</ref>。奥利弗还指出，特朗普自称曾谢绝参与《上周今夜秀》的邀请，但节目压根儿就没请过他，而且特朗普也根本不是像他声称的那样自付2016年竞选经费。总统候选人之女[[伊万卡·特朗普|伊万卡·特朗普]]曾在2003年纪录片《[[生为富人|生为富人]]》（''{{lang|en|Born Rich}}''）中表示，父亲曾自我描绘成比[[露宿者|无家可归的人]]还穷。<ref name="youtube-lwt20160228" /><ref name="time201603">{{cite journal | title = John Oliver Takes on Donald Trump On ''Last Week Tonight'' | url = http://time.com/4240734/john-oliver-donald-trump-last-week-tonight/ | first = Melissa | last = Locker | periodical = [[時代雜誌|Time]] | accessdate = 2019-06-05 | issn = 0040-781X | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20190605030610/http://time.com/4240734/john-oliver-donald-trump-last-week-tonight/ | archivedate = 2019-06-05 | journal =  }}</ref>

