主持人在节目最后呼吁观众用特朗普家族祖先的姓氏“德朗普夫”（{{lang|en|Drumpf}}）称呼总统候选人<ref name="youtube-lwt20160228" /><ref name="wpost20160229" />。奥利弗在节目前期指出，特朗普曾一再称呼犹太裔美国笑匠[[喬恩·史都華|喬恩·史都華]]的原名“乔纳森·莱博维茨”（{{lang|en|Jonathan Leibowitz}}）以示嘲讽，甚至于2013年5月在推特发文笑称史都華“应该对他的传统感到骄傲”，事后又矢口否认上述言论。曾与史都華在《[[每日秀|每日秀]]》中合作的奥利弗坚称总统候选人“应该对他的传统感到骄傲”，所以大家都应称他“唐纳德·德朗普夫”。奥利弗认为，这个姓氏更能反映特朗普的本质，那些认为他很有魅力、想把选票投给“承诺让美国再次伟大的人”的选民应该“先停下来好好想想，如果遇到的人名叫唐纳德·德朗普夫，他们会有什么感觉”。<ref name="youtube-lwt20160228" /><ref name="huffpo" />{{refn|group="注"|《[[波士頓環球報|波士頓環球報]]》曾于2015年发文谈论姓氏“德朗普夫”的影响，据品牌命名专家南希·弗里德曼（{{lang|en|Nancy Friedman}}）所述，德朗普夫最后两个字母“{{lang|en|pf}}”对说英语的人而言很难发音，而且开头的“{{lang|en|Dr}}”听起来也不像“特朗普”开头的“{{lang|en|Tr}}”那么鲜明，所以“德朗普夫”这样的姓氏“用英语说来几乎有些可笑”<ref name="TBG">{{cite news | url = https://www.bostonglobe.com/ideas/2015/09/09/why-donald-trump-better-than-donald-drumpf/7ltKCyRasCa5TY2l1Tr4HP/story.html | title = Why Donald Trump trumps Donald Drumpf | author = Britt Peterson | date = 2015-09-09 | accessdate = 2020-09-09 | newspaper = The Boston Globe | publisher = Boston Globe Media Partners | archive-date = 2019-11-08 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191108225421/https://www.bostonglobe.com/ideas/2015/09/09/why-donald-trump-better-than-donald-drumpf/7ltKCyRasCa5TY2l1Tr4HP/story.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。}}

奥利弗称，对于部分人士而言，“特朗普”似乎拥有强大等丰富的内涵，相比之下，总统候选人祖先的本姓德朗普夫就“远没有那么多神奇的魔力”，听起来“就像重度肥胖[[鸠鸽科|鸽子]]飞到[[法院拍賣房屋|倒闭抵押]][[老海军|老海军]]商店窗户上时发出的声音”，“又像瓶装零售品牌[[根汁啤酒|根汁啤酒]]从[[加油站|加油站]]小超市货架上摔下来的声音”。节目最后，奥利弗走向灯泡组成的“{{lang|en|DRUMPF}}”（“德朗普夫”）标识，提醒那些正在观看节目并有意投票支持特朗普的观众：“不要相信他说的那些东西去投票，他是胡扯大师。不要以为他很坚强，他就一巨婴，连手指都特别小。别以为他能搞什么建设，那完全就是烂透顶的生活品牌。”最后，奥利弗挑战特朗普，有种就因这场演出起诉。<ref name="youtube-lwt20160228" /><ref name="huffpo" />

[[特拉华州|特拉华州]]出现“德朗普夫工业”（{{lang|en|Drumpf Industries}}）[[有限公司|有限公司]]，并向[[美国专利及商标局|美国专利及商标局]]申请注册商标“德朗普夫”<ref name="wipreview">{{cite journal | title = 'Drumpf' trademark application filed | url = https://www.worldipreview.com/news/drumpf-trademark-application-filed-9643 | journal = World Intellectual Property Review | date = 2016-03-03 | accessdate = 2020-09-09 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180731153548/https://www.worldipreview.com/news/drumpf-trademark-application-filed-9643 | archivedate = 2018-07-31 }}</ref>。2016年5月，专利及商标局称该商标源于在世人物，即唐纳德·特朗普，注册申请中没有提供特朗普的书面同意书，所以拒绝申请<ref name="uspto" /><ref>{{cite news | title = Trump in second win as rejected 'Drumpf' TM gains no response | url = https://www.worldipreview.com/news/trump-in-second-win-as-rejected-drumpf-tm-gains-no-response-12535 | accessdate = 2020-09-09 | work = World Intellectual Property Review | date = 2016-11-18 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180731123851/https://www.worldipreview.com/news/trump-in-second-win-as-rejected-drumpf-tm-gains-no-response-12535 | archivedate = 2018-07-31 }}</ref>。节目播出后，奥利弗发布“{{lang|en|Drumpfinator}}”[[Google_Chrome|Google Chrome扩展程序]]，能把页面中的“{{lang|en|Trump}}”（“特朗普”）字样换成“{{lang|en|Drumpf}}”（“德朗普夫”）<ref name="db20160229" />。他还在节目期间创造并展示“#{{lang|en|MakeDonaldDrumpfAgain}}”（“让唐纳德变回德朗普夫”）[[主題標籤|主題標籤]]，之后又注册域名“{{lang|en|donaldjdrumpf.com}}”（“唐纳德德朗普夫.{{lang|en|com}}”），网站提供“{{lang|en|Drumpfinator}}”{{lang|en|Google Chrome}}扩展程序免费下载，同时出售印有口号“{{lang|en|Make Donald Drumpf Again}}”（“让唐纳德变回德朗普夫”）的棒球帽<ref name="huffpo" /><ref name="Explodes" />。帽子由联合服装（{{lang|en|Unionwear}}）生产<ref name=":2">{{cite news | url = https://blogs.wsj.com/washwire/2016/11/18/manufacturer-of-make-donald-drumpf-again-parody-hats-files-for-bankruptcy/ | title = Manufacturer of 'Make Donald Drumpf Again' Parody Hats Files for Bankruptcy | date = 2016-11-18 | newspaper = [[华尔街日报|The Wall Street Journal]] | last1 = Stech | first1 = Katy | accessdate = 2020-09-09 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20191222175439/https://blogs.wsj.com/washwire/2016/11/18/manufacturer-of-make-donald-drumpf-again-parody-hats-files-for-bankruptcy/ | archivedate = 2019-12-22 }}</ref>，以特朗普的“[[让美国再次伟大|让美国再次伟大]]”红色棒球帽为原型<ref name="huffpo" /><ref name="Explodes">{{cite news | url = https://www.nytimes.com/2016/03/09/business/media/trump-segment-on-john-oliver-show-explodes-on-youtube.html | title = John Oliver Sells Out of 'Make Donald Drumpf Again' Caps | date = 2016-03-09 | issn = 0362-4331 | newspaper = [[纽约时报|The New York Times]] | accessdate = 2020-09-09 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20190908133539/https://www.nytimes.com/2016/03/09/business/media/trump-segment-on-john-oliver-show-explodes-on-youtube.html | archivedate = 2019-09-08 }}</ref>。

== 反响 ==
节目播出后，“唐纳德·德朗普夫”的[[网络搜索引擎|互联网搜索]]呈[[病毒现象|病毒式爆发]]。节目播出两天后便是3月1日的初选“[[超級星期二|超級星期二]]”，“唐纳德·德朗普夫”[[Google搜索|Google搜索]]次数已超过与特朗鲁争夺共和党提名的[[泰德·克鲁兹|泰德·克鲁兹]]和[[馬可·魯比奧|馬可·魯比奧]]。<ref>{{cite news | title = 'Donald Drumpf' Is Beating Rubio and Cruz for Second in Google Searches | first = Justin | last = Wolfers | url = https://www.nytimes.com/2016/03/02/upshot/donald-drumpf-is-beating-rubio-and-cruz-for-second-in-web-searches.html | newspaper = [[纽约时报|The New York Times]] | issn = 0362-4331 | date = 2016-03-02 | accessdate = 2020-09-09 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200509081045/https://www.nytimes.com/2016/03/02/upshot/donald-drumpf-is-beating-rubio-and-cruz-for-second-in-web-searches.html | archivedate = 2020-05-09 }}</ref>其他媒体在《上周今夜秀》后马上跟进，报导特朗普“手指特别短”的消息<ref>{{cite news | title = Donald Trump's deep insecurity about his "short fingers", explained | last = Nelson | first = Libby | date = 2016-03-02 | publisher = Vox}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.vox.com/2016/3/2/11148356/donald-trump-short-fingers-small-hands-vulgarian | title = "Tiny hands", the insult that's been driving Donald Trump bonkers since 1988, explained | last = Nelson | first = Libby | date = 2016-06-17 | website = Vox | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200321233843/https://www.vox.com/2016/3/2/11148356/donald-trump-short-fingers-small-hands-vulgarian | archivedate = 2020-03-21 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2020-09-09 }}</ref>，以致特朗普于3月1日在推特宣称，根本没听过嘲笑他“手指特别短”的内容<ref>{{cite news | url = https://theweek.com/speedreads/609532/donald-trump-denies-knowing-anything-about-people-making-fun-small-finger | title = Donald Trump denies knowing anything about people making fun of his 'small fingers' | date = 2016-03-01 | periodical = The Week | accessdate = 2020-09-09 | deadurl = no | issn = 1533-8304 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180731093229/http://theweek.com/speedreads/609532/donald-trump-denies-knowing-anything-about-people-making-fun-small-finger | archivedate = 2018-07-31 }}</ref>。

截至3月4日，节目播出六天后，“{{lang|en|Drumpfinator}}”{{lang|en|Google Chrome}}扩展程序已有33.38万次下载和5800次查看<ref>{{cite news | title = Donald Drumpf browser extension installed more than 333K times | url = https://www.chicagotribune.com/entertainment/ct-donald-drumpf-chrome-extension-20160304-story.html | first = Tracy | last = Swartz | newspaper = [[芝加哥論壇報|Chicago Tribune]] | date = 2016-03-04 | accessdate = 2020-09-09 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20190415003506/https://www.chicagotribune.com/entertainment/ct-donald-drumpf-chrome-extension-20160304-story.html | archivedate = 2019-04-15 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。“{{lang|en|Drumpfinator}}”与其他类似扩展程序导致部分媒体误将特朗普印成德朗普夫后发布。[[美国犹太人大会|美国犹太人大会]]（{{lang|en|American Jewish Congress}}）一度在宣布会员民意调查结果时把共和党候选人称为“唐纳德·德朗普夫”，事后表示这是有人使用扩展程序导致<ref>{{cite web | title = 'Donald Drumpf' is runner-up in American Jewish Congress presidential poll | url = https://www.jta.org/2016/03/11/culture/donald-drumpf-listed-as-runner-up-in-american-jewish-congress-presidential-poll | first = Gabe | last = Friedman | agency = Jewish Telegraphic Agency | date = 2016-03-11 | accessdate = 2020-09-09 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20190623183200/https://www.jta.org/2016/03/11/culture/donald-drumpf-listed-as-runner-up-in-american-jewish-congress-presidential-poll | archivedate = 2019-06-23 }}</ref>。受另一种{{lang|en|Google Chrome}}扩展程序影响，《[[连线|连线]]》杂志文章用“某个手特小的人”代替特朗普的名字，意指“短指粗汉”[[網路迷因|网络模因]]<ref>{{cite news | url = https://observer.com/2016/03/wired-called-donald-trump-someone-with-tiny-hands-in-several-articles/ | title = Wired Called Donald Trump 'Someone With Tiny Hands' in Several Articles | last = Bonazzo | first = John | date = 2016-03-09 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20181118181035/https://observer.com/2016/03/wired-called-donald-trump-someone-with-tiny-hands-in-several-articles/ | archivedate = 2018-11-18 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2020-09-09 | periodical = [[纽约观察家报|The New York Observer]] }}</ref>。

